#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.ul.li:1128-9
msgid ""
"Unique <span class=\"ui\">Book map</span> to see a bird’s eye map of your "
"book including all your notes and highlights <a href=\"#L2-bookmap\" "
"class=\"internalink\"></a>"
msgstr ""
"Unieke <span class=\"ui\">Boekkaart</span> om een vogelvluchtkaart van het "
