"class=\"ui\">schermafdruk</span>-toets is <b>Alt + Shift + G</b>. Deze werkt "
"op alle schermen, modi en platforms. Op de Kindle 4 is het <b>Toetsenbord + "
"Menu</b>."

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.p:4062-21
msgid ""
"<span class=\"label_blue\">INFO</span> If you have a Kindle 4, <b>SHIFT</b> "
