"forumdisplay.php?f=276\">MobileRead forums</a>"
msgstr ""
"Andere KOReader‑gebruikers vinden op de <a href=\"https://www.mobileread.com/"
"forums/forumdisplay.php?f=276\">MobileRead‑forums</a>"

#: user_guide/en.html%2Bhtml.body.div.div.table.tr.td:5135-3
